        [Extent2].[Id] AS [Id1], 
        [Extent2].[FirstName] AS [FirstName], 
        [Extent2].[LastName] AS [LastName], 
        [Extent2].[BookId] AS [BookId], 
        [Extent2].[CreatedOn] AS [CreatedOn1], 
        [Extent2].[CreatedBy] AS [CreatedBy1], 
        [Extent2].[UpdatedOn] AS [UpdatedOn1], 
        [Extent2].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy1], 
        [Extent2].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted1], 
        CASE WHEN ([Extent2].[Id] IS NULL) THEN CAST(NULL AS int) ELSE 1 END AS [C1]
        FROM   (SELECT [Project1].[Id] AS [Id], [Project1].[Title] AS [Title], [Project1].[CountOfPage] AS [CountOfPage], [Project1].[Publisher] AS [Publisher], [Project1].[Year] AS [Year], [Project1].[ISBN] AS [ISBN], [Project1].[PicturePath] AS [PicturePath], [Project1].[CreatedOn] AS [CreatedOn], [Project1].[CreatedBy] AS [CreatedBy], [Project1].[UpdatedOn] AS [UpdatedOn], [Project1].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy], [Project1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted]
            FROM ( SELECT 
                @DynamicFilterParam_000001 AS [DynamicFilterParam_000001], 
                @DynamicFilterParam_000002 AS [DynamicFilterParam_000002], 
                [Extent1].[Id] AS [Id], 
                [Extent1].[Title] AS [Title], 
                [Extent1].[CountOfPage] AS [CountOfPage], 
                [Extent1].[Publisher] AS [Publisher], 
                [Extent1].[Year] AS [Year], 
                [Extent1].[ISBN] AS [ISBN], 
                [Extent1].[PicturePath] AS [PicturePath], 
                [Extent1].[CreatedOn] AS [CreatedOn], 
                [Extent1].[CreatedBy] AS [CreatedBy], 
                [Extent1].[UpdatedOn] AS [UpdatedOn], 
                [Extent1].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy], 
                [Extent1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted]
                FROM [dbo].[Books] AS [Extent1]
                WHERE ([Extent1].[IsDeleted] = @DynamicFilterParam_000001) 
            )  AS [Project1]
            ORDER BY [Project1].[Id] DESC
            OFFSET 0 ROWS FETCH NEXT 20 ROWS ONLY  ) AS [Limit1]
        LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Authors] AS [Extent2] ON ([Limit1].[Id] = [Extent2].[BookId]) AND (([Extent2].[IsDeleted] = @DynamicFilterParam_000001) )
    )  AS [Project2]
    ORDER BY [Project2].[Id] DESC, [Project2].[C1] ASC

        FROM   (SELECT [Project1].[Id] AS [Id], [Project1].[Title] AS [Title], [Project1].[CountOfPage] AS [CountOfPage], [Project1].[Publisher] AS [Publisher], [Project1].[Year] AS [Year], [Project1].[ISBN] AS [ISBN], [Project1].[PicturePath] AS [PicturePath], [Project1].[CreatedOn] AS [CreatedOn], [Project1].[CreatedBy] AS [CreatedBy], [Project1].[UpdatedOn] AS [UpdatedOn], [Project1].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy], [Project1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted]

                @DynamicFilterParam_000002 AS [DynamicFilterParam_000002],

                FROM [dbo].[Books] AS [Extent1]
                WHERE ([Extent1].[IsDeleted] = @DynamicFilterParam_000001) 
            )  AS [Project1]
            ORDER BY [Project1].[Id] DESC
            OFFSET 0 ROWS FETCH NEXT 20 ROWS ONLY  ) AS [Limit1]

        FROM   (SELECT [Project1].[Id] AS [Id], [Project1].[Title] AS [Title], [Project1].[CountOfPage] AS [CountOfPage], [Project1].[Publisher] AS [Publisher], [Project1].[Year] AS [Year], [Project1].[ISBN] AS [ISBN], [Project1].[PicturePath] AS [PicturePath], [Project1].[CreatedOn] AS [CreatedOn], [Project1].[CreatedBy] AS [CreatedBy], [Project1].[UpdatedOn] AS [UpdatedOn], [Project1].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy], [Project1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted]

                @DynamicFilterParam_000002 AS [DynamicFilterParam_000002],

                FROM [dbo].[Books] AS [Extent1]
                WHERE ([Extent1].[IsDeleted] = @DynamicFilterParam_000001) 
            )  AS [Project1]
            ORDER BY [Project1].[Id] DESC
            OFFSET 0 ROWS FETCH NEXT 20 ROWS ONLY  ) AS [Limit1]

        FROM   (SELECT [Project1].[Id] AS [Id], [Project1].[Title] AS [Title], [Project1].[CountOfPage] AS [CountOfPage], [Project1].[Publisher] AS [Publisher], [Project1].[Year] AS [Year], [Project1].[ISBN] AS [ISBN], [Project1].[PicturePath] AS [PicturePath], [Project1].[CreatedOn] AS [CreatedOn], [Project1].[CreatedBy] AS [CreatedBy], [Project1].[UpdatedOn] AS [UpdatedOn], [Project1].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy], [Project1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted]

                FROM [dbo].[Books] AS [Extent1]

            OFFSET 0 ROWS FETCH NEXT 20 ROWS ONLY  ) AS [Limit1]

        [Extent2].[LastName] AS [LastName],

        [Extent2].[CreatedBy] AS [CreatedBy1], 
        [Extent2].[UpdatedOn] AS [UpdatedOn1], 
        [Extent2].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy1], 
        [Extent2].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted1], 
        CASE WHEN ([Extent2].[Id] IS NULL) THEN CAST(NULL AS int) ELSE 1 END AS [C1]
        FROM   (SELECT [Project1].[Id] AS [Id], [Project1].[Title] AS [Title], [Project1].[CountOfPage] AS [CountOfPage], [Project1].[Publisher] AS [Publisher], [Project1].[Year] AS [Year], [Project1].[ISBN] AS [ISBN], [Project1].[PicturePath] AS [PicturePath], [Project1].[CreatedOn] AS [CreatedOn], [Project1].[CreatedBy] AS [CreatedBy], [Project1].[UpdatedOn] AS [UpdatedOn], [Project1].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy], [Project1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted]
            FROM ( SELECT 
                @DynamicFilterParam_000001 AS [DynamicFilterParam_000001], 
                @DynamicFilterParam_000002 AS [DynamicFilterParam_000002], 
                [Extent1].[Id] AS [Id], 
                [Extent1].[Title] AS [Title], 
                [Extent1].[CountOfPage] AS [CountOfPage], 
                [Extent1].[Publisher] AS [Publisher],

                [Extent1].[UpdatedOn] AS [UpdatedOn], 
                [Extent1].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy], 
                [Extent1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted]
                FROM [dbo].[Books] AS [Extent1]
                WHERE ([Extent1].[IsDeleted] = @DynamicFilterParam_000001) 
            )  AS [Project1]
            ORDER BY [Project1].[Id] DESC
            OFFSET 0 ROWS FETCH NEXT 20 ROWS ONLY  ) AS [Limit1]
        LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Authors] AS [Extent2] ON ([Limit1].[Id] = [Extent2].[BookId]) AND (([Extent2].[IsDeleted] = @DynamicFilterParam_000001) )
    )  AS [Project2]

        [Extent2].[Id] AS [Id1],

        [Extent2].[LastName] AS [LastName],

        [Extent2].[CreatedOn] AS [CreatedOn1], 
        [Extent2].[CreatedBy] AS [CreatedBy1], 
        [Extent2].[UpdatedOn] AS [UpdatedOn1], 
        [Extent2].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy1], 
        [Extent2].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted1], 
        CASE WHEN ([Extent2].[Id] IS NULL) THEN CAST(NULL AS int) ELSE 1 END AS [C1]
        FROM   (SELECT [Project1].[Id] AS [Id], [Project1].[Title] AS [Title], [Project1].[CountOfPage] AS [CountOfPage], [Project1].[Publisher] AS [Publisher], [Project1].[Year] AS [Year], [Project1].[ISBN] AS [ISBN], [Project1].[PicturePath] AS [PicturePath], [Project1].[CreatedOn] AS [CreatedOn], [Project1].[CreatedBy] AS [CreatedBy], [Project1].[UpdatedOn] AS [UpdatedOn], [Project1].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy], [Project1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted]

                [Extent1].[Id] AS [Id],

                FROM [dbo].[Books] AS [Extent1]
                WHERE ([Extent1].[IsDeleted] = @DynamicFilterParam_000001) 
            )  AS [Project1]
            ORDER BY [Project1].[Id] DESC

        FROM   (SELECT [Project1].[Id] AS [Id], [Project1].[Title] AS [Title], [Project1].[CountOfPage] AS [CountOfPage], [Project1].[Publisher] AS [Publisher], [Project1].[Year] AS [Year], [Project1].[ISBN] AS [ISBN], [Project1].[PicturePath] AS [PicturePath], [Project1].[CreatedOn] AS [CreatedOn], [Project1].[CreatedBy] AS [CreatedBy], [Project1].[UpdatedOn] AS [UpdatedOn], [Project1].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy], [Project1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted]

        [Extent2].[LastName] AS [LastName],

        [Extent2].[CreatedBy] AS [CreatedBy1], 
        [Extent2].[UpdatedOn] AS [UpdatedOn1], 
        [Extent2].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy1], 
        [Extent2].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted1], 
        CASE WHEN ([Extent2].[Id] IS NULL) THEN CAST(NULL AS int) ELSE 1 END AS [C1]
        FROM   (SELECT [Project1].[Id] AS [Id], [Project1].[Title] AS [Title], [Project1].[CountOfPage] AS [CountOfPage], [Project1].[Publisher] AS [Publisher], [Project1].[Year] AS [Year], [Project1].[ISBN] AS [ISBN], [Project1].[PicturePath] AS [PicturePath], [Project1].[CreatedOn] AS [CreatedOn], [Project1].[CreatedBy] AS [CreatedBy], [Project1].[UpdatedOn] AS [UpdatedOn], [Project1].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy], [Project1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted]

                @DynamicFilterParam_000002 AS [DynamicFilterParam_000002],

                [Extent1].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy], 
                [Extent1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted]
                FROM [dbo].[Books] AS [Extent1]
                WHERE ([Extent1].[IsDeleted] = @DynamicFilterParam_000001) 
            )  AS [Project1]
            ORDER BY [Project1].[Id] DESC
            OFFSET 0 ROWS FETCH NEXT 20 ROWS ONLY  ) AS [Limit1]

    [Project2].[IsDeleted1] AS [IsDeleted1]
    FROM ( SELECT 
        [Limit1].[Id] AS [Id], 
        [Limit1].[Title] AS [Title], 
        [Limit1].[CountOfPage] AS [CountOfPage], 
        [Limit1].[Publisher] AS [Publisher], 
        [Limit1].[Year] AS [Year], 
        [Limit1].[ISBN] AS [ISBN], 
        [Limit1].[PicturePath] AS [PicturePath], 
        [Limit1].[CreatedOn] AS [CreatedOn], 
        [Limit1].[CreatedBy] AS [CreatedBy], 
        [Limit1].[UpdatedOn] AS [UpdatedOn], 
        [Limit1].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy], 
        [Limit1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted], 
        [Extent2].[Id] AS [Id1], 
        [Extent2].[FirstName] AS [FirstName], 
        [Extent2].[LastName] AS [LastName], 
        [Extent2].[BookId] AS [BookId], 
        [Extent2].[CreatedOn] AS [CreatedOn1], 
        [Extent2].[CreatedBy] AS [CreatedBy1], 
        [Extent2].[UpdatedOn] AS [UpdatedOn1], 
        [Extent2].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy1], 
        [Extent2].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted1], 
        CASE WHEN ([Extent2].[Id] IS NULL) THEN CAST(NULL AS int) ELSE 1 END AS [C1]
        FROM   (SELECT [Project1].[Id] AS [Id], [Project1].[Title] AS [Title], [Project1].[CountOfPage] AS [CountOfPage], [Project1].[Publisher] AS [Publisher], [Project1].[Year] AS [Year], [Project1].[ISBN] AS [ISBN], [Project1].[PicturePath] AS [PicturePath], [Project1].[CreatedOn] AS [CreatedOn], [Project1].[CreatedBy] AS [CreatedBy], [Project1].[UpdatedOn] AS [UpdatedOn], [Project1].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy], [Project1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted]
            FROM ( SELECT 
                @DynamicFilterParam_000001 AS [DynamicFilterParam_000001], 
                @DynamicFilterParam_000002 AS [DynamicFilterParam_000002], 
                [Extent1].[Id] AS [Id], 
                [Extent1].[Title] AS [Title], 
                [Extent1].[CountOfPage] AS [CountOfPage], 
                [Extent1].[Publisher] AS [Publisher], 
                [Extent1].[Year] AS [Year], 
                [Extent1].[ISBN] AS [ISBN], 
                [Extent1].[PicturePath] AS [PicturePath], 
                [Extent1].[CreatedOn] AS [CreatedOn], 
                [Extent1].[CreatedBy] AS [CreatedBy], 
                [Extent1].[UpdatedOn] AS [UpdatedOn], 
                [Extent1].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy], 
                [Extent1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted]
                FROM [dbo].[Books] AS [Extent1]
                WHERE ([Extent1].[IsDeleted] = @DynamicFilterParam_000001) 
            )  AS [Project1]
            ORDER BY [Project1].[Id] DESC
            OFFSET 0 ROWS FETCH NEXT 20 ROWS ONLY  ) AS [Limit1]
        LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Authors] AS [Extent2] ON ([Limit1].[Id] = [Extent2].[BookId]) AND (([Extent2].[IsDeleted] = @DynamicFilterParam_000001) )
    )  AS [Project2]
    ORDER BY [Project2].[Id] DESC, [Project2].[C1] ASC

        FROM   (SELECT [Project1].[Id] AS [Id], [Project1].[Title] AS [Title], [Project1].[CountOfPage] AS [CountOfPage], [Project1].[Publisher] AS [Publisher], [Project1].[Year] AS [Year], [Project1].[ISBN] AS [ISBN], [Project1].[PicturePath] AS [PicturePath], [Project1].[CreatedOn] AS [CreatedOn], [Project1].[CreatedBy] AS [CreatedBy], [Project1].[UpdatedOn] AS [UpdatedOn], [Project1].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy], [Project1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted]

    FROM ( SELECT 
        [Limit1].[Id] AS [Id], 
        [Limit1].[Title] AS [Title], 
        [Limit1].[CountOfPage] AS [CountOfPage], 
        [Limit1].[Publisher] AS [Publisher], 
        [Limit1].[Year] AS [Year], 
        [Limit1].[ISBN] AS [ISBN], 
        [Limit1].[PicturePath] AS [PicturePath], 
        [Limit1].[CreatedOn] AS [CreatedOn], 
        [Limit1].[CreatedBy] AS [CreatedBy], 
        [Limit1].[UpdatedOn] AS [UpdatedOn], 
        [Limit1].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy], 
        [Limit1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted], 
        [Extent2].[Id] AS [Id1], 
        [Extent2].[FirstName] AS [FirstName], 
        [Extent2].[LastName] AS [LastName], 
        [Extent2].[BookId] AS [BookId], 
        [Extent2].[CreatedOn] AS [CreatedOn1], 
        [Extent2].[CreatedBy] AS [CreatedBy1], 
        [Extent2].[UpdatedOn] AS [UpdatedOn1], 
        [Extent2].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy1], 
        [Extent2].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted1], 
        CASE WHEN ([Extent2].[Id] IS NULL) THEN CAST(NULL AS int) ELSE 1 END AS [C1]
        FROM   (SELECT [Project1].[Id] AS [Id], [Project1].[Title] AS [Title], [Project1].[CountOfPage] AS [CountOfPage], [Project1].[Publisher] AS [Publisher], [Project1].[Year] AS [Year], [Project1].[ISBN] AS [ISBN], [Project1].[PicturePath] AS [PicturePath], [Project1].[CreatedOn] AS [CreatedOn], [Project1].[CreatedBy] AS [CreatedBy], [Project1].[UpdatedOn] AS [UpdatedOn], [Project1].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy], [Project1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted]
            FROM ( SELECT 
                @DynamicFilterParam_000001 AS [DynamicFilterParam_000001], 
                @DynamicFilterParam_000002 AS [DynamicFilterParam_000002], 
                [Extent1].[Id] AS [Id], 
                [Extent1].[Title] AS [Title], 
                [Extent1].[CountOfPage] AS [CountOfPage], 
                [Extent1].[Publisher] AS [Publisher], 
                [Extent1].[Year] AS [Year], 
                [Extent1].[ISBN] AS [ISBN], 
                [Extent1].[PicturePath] AS [PicturePath], 
                [Extent1].[CreatedOn] AS [CreatedOn], 
                [Extent1].[CreatedBy] AS [CreatedBy], 
                [Extent1].[UpdatedOn] AS [UpdatedOn], 
                [Extent1].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy], 
                [Extent1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted]
                FROM [dbo].[Books] AS [Extent1]
                WHERE ([Extent1].[IsDeleted] = @DynamicFilterParam_000001) 
            )  AS [Project1]
            ORDER BY [Project1].[Title] DESC
            OFFSET 0 ROWS FETCH NEXT 20 ROWS ONLY  ) AS [Limit1]
        LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Authors] AS [Extent2] ON ([Limit1].[Id] = [Extent2].[BookId]) AND (([Extent2].[IsDeleted] = @DynamicFilterParam_000001) )
    )  AS [Project2]
    ORDER BY [Project2].[Title] DESC, [Project2].[Id] ASC, [Project2].[C1] ASC

        [Limit1].[Title] AS [Title],

        [Limit1].[Publisher] AS [Publisher],

        [Limit1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted], 
        [Extent2].[Id] AS [Id1],

        [Extent2].[LastName] AS [LastName],

        [Extent2].[UpdatedOn] AS [UpdatedOn1], 
        [Extent2].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy1], 
        [Extent2].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted1], 
        CASE WHEN ([Extent2].[Id] IS NULL) THEN CAST(NULL AS int) ELSE 1 END AS [C1]
        FROM   (SELECT [Project1].[Id] AS [Id], [Project1].[Title] AS [Title], [Project1].[CountOfPage] AS [CountOfPage], [Project1].[Publisher] AS [Publisher], [Project1].[Year] AS [Year], [Project1].[ISBN] AS [ISBN], [Project1].[PicturePath] AS [PicturePath], [Project1].[CreatedOn] AS [CreatedOn], [Project1].[CreatedBy] AS [CreatedBy], [Project1].[UpdatedOn] AS [UpdatedOn], [Project1].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy], [Project1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted]
            FROM ( SELECT 
                @DynamicFilterParam_000001 AS [DynamicFilterParam_000001], 
                @DynamicFilterParam_000002 AS [DynamicFilterParam_000002], 
                [Extent1].[Id] AS [Id], 
                [Extent1].[Title] AS [Title],

                [Extent1].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy], 
                [Extent1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted]
                FROM [dbo].[Books] AS [Extent1]
                WHERE ([Extent1].[IsDeleted] = @DynamicFilterParam_000001) 
            )  AS [Project1]
            ORDER BY [Project1].[Id] DESC
            OFFSET 0 ROWS FETCH NEXT 20 ROWS ONLY  ) AS [Limit1]

    )  AS [Project2]

        [Extent2].[LastName] AS [LastName],

        [Extent2].[CreatedBy] AS [CreatedBy1], 
        [Extent2].[UpdatedOn] AS [UpdatedOn1], 
        [Extent2].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy1], 
        [Extent2].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted1], 
        CASE WHEN ([Extent2].[Id] IS NULL) THEN CAST(NULL AS int) ELSE 1 END AS [C1]
        FROM   (SELECT [Project1].[Id] AS [Id], [Project1].[Title] AS [Title], [Project1].[CountOfPage] AS [CountOfPage], [Project1].[Publisher] AS [Publisher], [Project1].[Year] AS [Year], [Project1].[ISBN] AS [ISBN], [Project1].[PicturePath] AS [PicturePath], [Project1].[CreatedOn] AS [CreatedOn], [Project1].[CreatedBy] AS [CreatedBy], [Project1].[UpdatedOn] AS [UpdatedOn], [Project1].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy], [Project1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted]

                [Extent1].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy],

                FROM [dbo].[Books] AS [Extent1]
                WHERE ([Extent1].[IsDeleted] = @DynamicFilterParam_000001) 
            )  AS [Project1]
            ORDER BY [Project1].[Id] ASC
            OFFSET 0 ROWS FETCH NEXT 20 ROWS ONLY  ) AS [Limit1]

                WHERE ([Extent1].[IsDeleted] = @DynamicFilterParam_000001)

            OFFSET 20 ROWS FETCH NEXT 20 ROWS ONLY  ) AS [Limit1]

    )  AS [Project2]

        FROM   (SELECT [Project1].[Id] AS [Id], [Project1].[Title] AS [Title], [Project1].[CountOfPage] AS [CountOfPage], [Project1].[Publisher] AS [Publisher], [Project1].[Year] AS [Year], [Project1].[ISBN] AS [ISBN], [Project1].[PicturePath] AS [PicturePath], [Project1].[CreatedOn] AS [CreatedOn], [Project1].[CreatedBy] AS [CreatedBy], [Project1].[UpdatedOn] AS [UpdatedOn], [Project1].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy], [Project1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted]

        [Extent2].[LastName] AS [LastName],

        [Extent2].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy1], 
        [Extent2].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted1], 
        CASE WHEN ([Extent2].[Id] IS NULL) THEN CAST(NULL AS int) ELSE 1 END AS [C1]
        FROM   (SELECT [Project1].[Id] AS [Id], [Project1].[Title] AS [Title], [Project1].[CountOfPage] AS [CountOfPage], [Project1].[Publisher] AS [Publisher], [Project1].[Year] AS [Year], [Project1].[ISBN] AS [ISBN], [Project1].[PicturePath] AS [PicturePath], [Project1].[CreatedOn] AS [CreatedOn], [Project1].[CreatedBy] AS [CreatedBy], [Project1].[UpdatedOn] AS [UpdatedOn], [Project1].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy], [Project1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted]
            FROM ( SELECT 
                @DynamicFilterParam_000001 AS [DynamicFilterParam_000001], 
                @DynamicFilterParam_000002 AS [DynamicFilterParam_000002], 
                [Extent1].[Id] AS [Id], 
                [Extent1].[Title] AS [Title], 
                [Extent1].[CountOfPage] AS [CountOfPage], 
                [Extent1].[Publisher] AS [Publisher], 
                [Extent1].[Year] AS [Year], 
                [Extent1].[ISBN] AS [ISBN], 
                [Extent1].[PicturePath] AS [PicturePath], 
                [Extent1].[CreatedOn] AS [CreatedOn], 
                [Extent1].[CreatedBy] AS [CreatedBy], 
                [Extent1].[UpdatedOn] AS [UpdatedOn], 
                [Extent1].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy], 
                [Extent1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted]
                FROM [dbo].[Books] AS [Extent1]
                WHERE ([Extent1].[IsDeleted] = @DynamicFilterParam_000001) 
            )  AS [Project1]
            ORDER BY [Project1].[Title] ASC
            OFFSET 20 ROWS FETCH NEXT 20 ROWS ONLY  ) AS [Limit1]
        LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Authors] AS [Extent2] ON ([Limit1].[Id] = [Extent2].[BookId]) AND (([Extent2].[IsDeleted] = @DynamicFilterParam_000001) )
    )  AS [Project2]
    ORDER BY [Project2].[Title] ASC, [Project2].[Id] ASC, [Project2].[C1] ASC

        FROM   (SELECT [Project1].[Id] AS [Id], [Project1].[Title] AS [Title], [Project1].[CountOfPage] AS [CountOfPage], [Project1].[Publisher] AS [Publisher], [Project1].[Year] AS [Year], [Project1].[ISBN] AS [ISBN], [Project1].[PicturePath] AS [PicturePath], [Project1].[CreatedOn] AS [CreatedOn], [Project1].[CreatedBy] AS [CreatedBy], [Project1].[UpdatedOn] AS [UpdatedOn], [Project1].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy], [Project1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted]

                FROM [dbo].[Books] AS [Extent1]
                WHERE ([Extent1].[IsDeleted] = @DynamicFilterParam_000001) 
            )  AS [Project1]
            ORDER BY [Project1].[Id] ASC
            OFFSET 0 ROWS FETCH NEXT 20 ROWS ONLY  ) AS [Limit1]

        [Limit1].[CreatedOn] AS [CreatedOn], 
        [Limit1].[CreatedBy] AS [CreatedBy], 
        [Limit1].[UpdatedOn] AS [UpdatedOn], 
        [Limit1].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy],

        [Extent2].[LastName] AS [LastName], 
        [Extent2].[BookId] AS [BookId],

        [Extent2].[CreatedBy] AS [CreatedBy1], 
        [Extent2].[UpdatedOn] AS [UpdatedOn1], 
        [Extent2].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy1], 
        [Extent2].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted1], 
        CASE WHEN ([Extent2].[Id] IS NULL) THEN CAST(NULL AS int) ELSE 1 END AS [C1]
        FROM   (SELECT [Project1].[Id] AS [Id], [Project1].[Title] AS [Title], [Project1].[CountOfPage] AS [CountOfPage], [Project1].[Publisher] AS [Publisher], [Project1].[Year] AS [Year], [Project1].[ISBN] AS [ISBN], [Project1].[PicturePath] AS [PicturePath], [Project1].[CreatedOn] AS [CreatedOn], [Project1].[CreatedBy] AS [CreatedBy], [Project1].[UpdatedOn] AS [UpdatedOn], [Project1].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy], [Project1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted]
            FROM ( SELECT 
                @DynamicFilterParam_000001 AS [DynamicFilterParam_000001], 
                @DynamicFilterParam_000002 AS [DynamicFilterParam_000002], 
                [Extent1].[Id] AS [Id], 
                [Extent1].[Title] AS [Title], 
                [Extent1].[CountOfPage] AS [CountOfPage], 
                [Extent1].[Publisher] AS [Publisher], 
                [Extent1].[Year] AS [Year], 
                [Extent1].[ISBN] AS [ISBN],

                [Extent1].[CreatedBy] AS [CreatedBy], 
                [Extent1].[UpdatedOn] AS [UpdatedOn], 
                [Extent1].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy], 
                [Extent1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted]
                FROM [dbo].[Books] AS [Extent1]
                WHERE ([Extent1].[IsDeleted] = @DynamicFilterParam_000001) 
            )  AS [Project1]
            ORDER BY [Project1].[Title] DESC
            OFFSET 0 ROWS FETCH NEXT 20 ROWS ONLY  ) AS [Limit1]
        LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Authors] AS [Extent2] ON ([Limit1].[Id] = [Extent2].[BookId]) AND (([Extent2].[IsDeleted] = @DynamicFilterParam_000001) )
    )  AS [Project2]
    ORDER BY [Project2].[Title] DESC, [Project2].[Id] ASC, [Project2].[C1] ASC

        CASE WHEN ([Extent2].[Id] IS NULL) THEN CAST(NULL AS int) ELSE 1 END AS [C1]
        FROM   (SELECT [Project1].[Id] AS [Id], [Project1].[Title] AS [Title], [Project1].[CountOfPage] AS [CountOfPage], [Project1].[Publisher] AS [Publisher], [Project1].[Year] AS [Year], [Project1].[ISBN] AS [ISBN], [Project1].[PicturePath] AS [PicturePath], [Project1].[CreatedOn] AS [CreatedOn], [Project1].[CreatedBy] AS [CreatedBy], [Project1].[UpdatedOn] AS [UpdatedOn], [Project1].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy], [Project1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted]
            FROM ( SELECT 
                @DynamicFilterParam_000001 AS [DynamicFilterParam_000001], 
                @DynamicFilterParam_000002 AS [DynamicFilterParam_000002], 
                [Extent1].[Id] AS [Id], 
                [Extent1].[Title] AS [Title], 
                [Extent1].[CountOfPage] AS [CountOfPage], 
                [Extent1].[Publisher] AS [Publisher], 
                [Extent1].[Year] AS [Year], 
                [Extent1].[ISBN] AS [ISBN], 
                [Extent1].[PicturePath] AS [PicturePath], 
                [Extent1].[CreatedOn] AS [CreatedOn], 
                [Extent1].[CreatedBy] AS [CreatedBy], 
                [Extent1].[UpdatedOn] AS [UpdatedOn], 
                [Extent1].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy], 
                [Extent1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted]
                FROM [dbo].[Books] AS [Extent1]
                WHERE ([Extent1].[IsDeleted] = @DynamicFilterParam_000001) 
            )  AS [Project1]
            ORDER BY [Project1].[Id] ASC
            OFFSET 0 ROWS FETCH NEXT 20 ROWS ONLY  ) AS [Limit1]
        LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Authors] AS [Extent2] ON ([Limit1].[Id] = [Extent2].[BookId]) AND (([Extent2].[IsDeleted] = @DynamicFilterParam_000001) )
    )  AS [Project2]
    ORDER BY [Project2].[Id] ASC, [Project2].[C1] ASC

        FROM   (SELECT [Project1].[Id] AS [Id], [Project1].[Title] AS [Title], [Project1].[CountOfPage] AS [CountOfPage], [Project1].[Publisher] AS [Publisher], [Project1].[Year] AS [Year], [Project1].[ISBN] AS [ISBN], [Project1].[PicturePath] AS [PicturePath], [Project1].[CreatedOn] AS [CreatedOn], [Project1].[CreatedBy] AS [CreatedBy], [Project1].[UpdatedOn] AS [UpdatedOn], [Project1].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy], [Project1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted]

                @DynamicFilterParam_000002 AS [DynamicFilterParam_000002],

                WHERE ([Extent1].[IsDeleted] = @DynamicFilterParam_000001) 
            )  AS [Project1]

            OFFSET 0 ROWS FETCH NEXT 20 ROWS ONLY  ) AS [Limit1]

        [Limit1].[Title] AS [Title], 
        [Limit1].[CountOfPage] AS [CountOfPage], 
        [Limit1].[Publisher] AS [Publisher], 
        [Limit1].[Year] AS [Year],

        [Limit1].[PicturePath] AS [PicturePath], 
        [Limit1].[CreatedOn] AS [CreatedOn], 
        [Limit1].[CreatedBy] AS [CreatedBy], 
        [Limit1].[UpdatedOn] AS [UpdatedOn], 
        [Limit1].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy], 
        [Limit1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted], 
        [Extent2].[Id] AS [Id1], 
        [Extent2].[FirstName] AS [FirstName], 
        [Extent2].[LastName] AS [LastName], 
        [Extent2].[BookId] AS [BookId], 
        [Extent2].[CreatedOn] AS [CreatedOn1], 
        [Extent2].[CreatedBy] AS [CreatedBy1], 
        [Extent2].[UpdatedOn] AS [UpdatedOn1], 
        [Extent2].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy1], 
        [Extent2].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted1], 
        CASE WHEN ([Extent2].[Id] IS NULL) THEN CAST(NULL AS int) ELSE 1 END AS [C1]
        FROM   (SELECT [Project1].[Id] AS [Id], [Project1].[Title] AS [Title], [Project1].[CountOfPage] AS [CountOfPage], [Project1].[Publisher] AS [Publisher], [Project1].[Year] AS [Year], [Project1].[ISBN] AS [ISBN], [Project1].[PicturePath] AS [PicturePath], [Project1].[CreatedOn] AS [CreatedOn], [Project1].[CreatedBy] AS [CreatedBy], [Project1].[UpdatedOn] AS [UpdatedOn], [Project1].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy], [Project1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted]
            FROM ( SELECT 
                @DynamicFilterParam_000001 AS [DynamicFilterParam_000001], 
                @DynamicFilterParam_000002 AS [DynamicFilterParam_000002], 
                [Extent1].[Id] AS [Id], 
                [Extent1].[Title] AS [Title], 
                [Extent1].[CountOfPage] AS [CountOfPage], 
                [Extent1].[Publisher] AS [Publisher],

                [Extent1].[CreatedBy] AS [CreatedBy], 
                [Extent1].[UpdatedOn] AS [UpdatedOn], 
                [Extent1].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy], 
                [Extent1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted]
                FROM [dbo].[Books] AS [Extent1]
                WHERE ([Extent1].[IsDeleted] = @DynamicFilterParam_000001) 
            )  AS [Project1]
            ORDER BY [Project1].[Id] ASC
            OFFSET 0 ROWS FETCH NEXT 20 ROWS ONLY  ) AS [Limit1]
        LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Authors] AS [Extent2] ON ([Limit1].[Id] = [Extent2].[BookId]) AND (([Extent2].[IsDeleted] = @DynamicFilterParam_000001) )
    )  AS [Project2]

    [Project2].[UpdatedBy1] AS [UpdatedBy1], 
    [Project2].[IsDeleted1] AS [IsDeleted1]
    FROM ( SELECT 
        [Limit1].[Id] AS [Id], 
        [Limit1].[Title] AS [Title], 
        [Limit1].[CountOfPage] AS [CountOfPage], 
        [Limit1].[Publisher] AS [Publisher], 
        [Limit1].[Year] AS [Year], 
        [Limit1].[ISBN] AS [ISBN], 
        [Limit1].[PicturePath] AS [PicturePath], 
        [Limit1].[CreatedOn] AS [CreatedOn], 
        [Limit1].[CreatedBy] AS [CreatedBy], 
        [Limit1].[UpdatedOn] AS [UpdatedOn], 
        [Limit1].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy], 
        [Limit1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted], 
        [Extent2].[Id] AS [Id1], 
        [Extent2].[FirstName] AS [FirstName], 
        [Extent2].[LastName] AS [LastName], 
        [Extent2].[BookId] AS [BookId], 
        [Extent2].[CreatedOn] AS [CreatedOn1], 
        [Extent2].[CreatedBy] AS [CreatedBy1], 
        [Extent2].[UpdatedOn] AS [UpdatedOn1], 
        [Extent2].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy1], 
        [Extent2].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted1], 
        CASE WHEN ([Extent2].[Id] IS NULL) THEN CAST(NULL AS int) ELSE 1 END AS [C1]
        FROM   (SELECT [Project1].[Id] AS [Id], [Project1].[Title] AS [Title], [Project1].[CountOfPage] AS [CountOfPage], [Project1].[Publisher] AS [Publisher], [Project1].[Year] AS [Year], [Project1].[ISBN] AS [ISBN], [Project1].[PicturePath] AS [PicturePath], [Project1].[CreatedOn] AS [CreatedOn], [Project1].[CreatedBy] AS [CreatedBy], [Project1].[UpdatedOn] AS [UpdatedOn], [Project1].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy], [Project1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted]
            FROM ( SELECT 
                @DynamicFilterParam_000001 AS [DynamicFilterParam_000001], 
                @DynamicFilterParam_000002 AS [DynamicFilterParam_000002], 
                [Extent1].[Id] AS [Id], 
                [Extent1].[Title] AS [Title], 
                [Extent1].[CountOfPage] AS [CountOfPage], 
                [Extent1].[Publisher] AS [Publisher], 
                [Extent1].[Year] AS [Year], 
                [Extent1].[ISBN] AS [ISBN], 
                [Extent1].[PicturePath] AS [PicturePath], 
                [Extent1].[CreatedOn] AS [CreatedOn], 
                [Extent1].[CreatedBy] AS [CreatedBy], 
                [Extent1].[UpdatedOn] AS [UpdatedOn], 
                [Extent1].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy], 
                [Extent1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted]
                FROM [dbo].[Books] AS [Extent1]
                WHERE ([Extent1].[IsDeleted] = @DynamicFilterParam_000001) 
            )  AS [Project1]
            ORDER BY [Project1].[Title] DESC
            OFFSET 0 ROWS FETCH NEXT 20 ROWS ONLY  ) AS [Limit1]
        LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Authors] AS [Extent2] ON ([Limit1].[Id] = [Extent2].[BookId]) AND (([Extent2].[IsDeleted] = @DynamicFilterParam_000001) )
    )  AS [Project2]
    ORDER BY [Project2].[Title] DESC, [Project2].[Id] ASC, [Project2].[C1] ASC
